Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.48,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGilles' Comic Font\bord0\c&H867B6C&\an1\blur0.4\b0\shad0\fs28\frx10\fry8\frz2.5\move(126.886,278,-71.373,278,0,2460)}Physical\N Exam\N Site
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody lined up here,\Nplease take all your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:40.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fine, you want us to take \Nour clothes off, all right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:41.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Take them all off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Got them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, those who took\Ntheir clothes off, please sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,First I'm going to use a stethoscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'll be a little cold, but bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:59.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.\N Why am I calmly using the stethoscope?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:05.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors about Cromartie High School,\Nbut this is even worse than what I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter what appears,\Nit shouldn't be surprising,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:12.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but why does it have to be\N like this right from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I'm a veteran doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:19.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter what shows up,\NI should just perform my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:24.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But from an outside perspective,\Nthis looks really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't good.\NStop thinking such foolish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Focus on the medical exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:34.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could you turn around\N so I can see your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That IS my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't tell the difference\N between his front and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:47.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I'll pull myself together\Nand go to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if speaking Japanese would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Could you look this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:00.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems that he understands the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, there's nothing wrong.\NYou're in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I can't lower my guard yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know what else might show up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What if a demon or a bear appears?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:29.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I could at least deal with it\Nif it were a gorilla or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness that it's a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness it's a gorilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As I thought, a gorilla's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right! A gorilla's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, thank goodness it was a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Doctor, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.75,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's the matter, Mechazawa?\NYou look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:08.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I got the results from \Nthe physical exam from the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:13.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The doctor says, "Have a thorough\N checkup at a different hospital."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:16.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm known as a calm man, but even I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm so concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I tested positive for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Tested positive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:22.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:28.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think you've got\Na terrible disease or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but, how do I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think you should\Nworry about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:32.46,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnGilles' Comic Font\fs28\bord0\blur0.5\b0\shad0\c&H191944&\pos(498.481,440)}Guts
