Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:36.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That doctor gave me a reference\Nto a different hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't be of much help, though.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial\fs22\an7\c&H9AE8F3&\bord0\pos(95.165,10)\blur0.5\frz1}Personal Computers\NAudio\NCamera
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial\fs22\an7\c\c&H045F8C&\bord0\blur0.4\pos(98.563,13)\frz1}Personal Computers\NAudio\NCamera
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\3c&H0E5D77&\fnHand Drawn Shapes\fs24\b0\c&HC7E6FF&\bord0.2\be1\frz334\pos(374.994,170)}Cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\3c&H0E5D77&\fnHand Drawn Shapes\fs24\b0\c&HC7E6FF&\bord0.2\blur1\frz334\pos(412.38,119)}Dirt{}
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fscx101.962\shad0\fnArial\fs24\bord20\an9\c&HC8D5ED&\3c&H4062F5&\be2\frz1.562\pos(569.854,86)\clip(m 462.25 86 l 572.125 84 573.25 170 454.25 173 458.875 170 481.5 163 466.75 145 483.75 127 461.125 116 473.5 99 445.25 92 445.25 86)\frx4\fry356}Hiromoto\N{\fs20} Home\N Appliances
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.76,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs24\shad0\fnArial\bord3\b0\be4\c&H000000&\3c&H7266C4&\pos(244.709,267)}Going\N out of\N business\N sale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:50.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the address, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:55.44,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\shad0\bord0\c&HDBEFE8&\fs48\frx16\fry0\pos(419.177,188)}Satou Electronics Store
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Did I write down the wrong lot number?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I think this is probably the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:05:00.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, there are lots of doctors\Nwho also own electronics stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Are there such doctors?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, in any case, why don't we go in?\NWe can talk after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:15.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... We brought him here\Nwith his doctor's reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, that. Yeah, I've heard all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It looks like this is an older model,\Nbut if we fix it good, you can still use it fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well... that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:29.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Youngsters these days carelessly toss\Nthings away once they get a little beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:32.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't it sad when the owners\Ndon't care about their machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Machines have hearts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I understand that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, do you have a warranty certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A warranty certificate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean health insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then it might be better to\Ncontact the manufacturer directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this guy really a doctor?\NHe's starting to tick me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This doctor just talks rough, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,People often say that the rougher a man talks,\Nthe more skilled he is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, just leave it to me!\NI'll at least do the maintenance work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll wait for you outside, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur0.4\shad0\bord0\c&HDBEFE8&\fs78\frx38\fry332\pos(450.899,256)\frz29.997}Satou Electronics Store
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad that you feel\Nbetter now, Mechazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're relieved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please input your name following\Nthe voice instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A password will be set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:29.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please try to avoid using\N personal information such as your birth date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The data's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:37.62,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Maeda's house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:37.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}There was a birthday party\N going on at Maeda's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:48.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:56.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, dear Freddie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}So why are you doing it at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're such a cold person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I worked hard getting ready for this, Maeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you really know when Freddie's birthday is?\NDid you ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, since we don't know when it is,\Nwe decided it's today on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:15.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:19.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:23.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, dear Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's happy birthday, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Yutaka Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:36.64,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(420,0)\pos(354.601,392)}Yutaka Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I may be repeating this too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}but I'm the boss of Year 1\N at Cromartie, and its strongest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}I'm strong in fighting,\N but I get motion sickness easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They told me that they'd\Nhold a birthday party for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:45.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,so I made the mistake of coming without\Nthinking too much because I just felt happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:48.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But the one problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:49.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(421.443,60,405.582,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:49.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(388.589,60,373.294,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:50.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(355.734,60,339.873,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:50.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(325.146,60,309.285,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:51.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(292.291,60,276.43,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:51.82,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(258.304,60,243.576,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:52.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5651CA&\fs30\blur0.8\shad0\fnArial\move(226.582,60,210.722,60,0,250)}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.57,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Birthday Party Site
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's being held on a houseboat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble! Takenouchi fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here, tempura's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Tempura again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now he's being violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Freddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Takenouchi, he's not the boatman.\NYou can't hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnSet Fire to the Rain\pos(368.196,115)\fs75\c&H80D5C8&\be2\b1}Killer Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:08.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnSet Fire to the Rain\pos(368.196,35)\fs75\c&H80D5C8&\be2\b1}Killer Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The reason I asked you to gather here today
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:18.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,is solely because I would like it to be clear\Nabout who among us is the strongest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The Mohawk occasionally has a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's just what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll accept a challenge from anyone, anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:31.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm opposed to such violence.\NWe should discuss it peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:37.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I totally understand the idea\N of deciding who's the strongest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:40.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I understand that feeling very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's one thing that I wanna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:48.00,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\be2\pos(597.044,52)}Maeda's\N house
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't really have to do it\Nat my house, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:52.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why do you always gotta be a party pooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We just replaced the tatami mat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't gather at my house without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't open the fridge without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't eat a banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's your cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! To decide who's the strongest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:07.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,a one-on-one fight is the best, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:12.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll make them regret rushing\Ntowards their death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:14.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, the first fight will be Maeda vs Gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forget that! Why do you just\Ndecide without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're standing out big time today, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course I am! This is my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's a bother, so there's no way\Nyou're going on a rampage in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you really want to do it,\Ngo outside and do it there! I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:29.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's cold outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:32.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you don't stop complaining, I'll call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:36.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then let's decide who's\N the strongest man through discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:38.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I want to go on a rampage here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll really fudging kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:49.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll make it clear who's the\Nstrongest man in the Hokuto Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hokuto Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:55.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying among all the confusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? It's not?\N Aren't you guys in the Hokuto Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, in a way, Mr. Hokuto\Nis suitable as our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:06.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In this world I think it's okay that the first one\Nto say it wins, regardless of actual ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:10.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that's not why I said Hokuto Corps...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:14.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know who's the strongest,\Nbut it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:18.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, with all of these members\Ngathered here, we need fear nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When you really think about it,\Nthese are incredible members.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:25.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right! There's no doubt that we can defeat\Nany vicious enemy with these members!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:30.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That means that we have\Nnothing in this world to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's my old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,She's really scary!
