Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There are many more people who\Nhave not appeared yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't mean anyone\Nwill appear in the next episode.
